#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
int isleap(int y){
  return (y%400==0 || (y%4==0 && y%100!=0));  
}
int main(){
  int t,d,y,i,lp,n,n1,cn;
  string s,s1,s2;
  string mth[]={"Hundreds","Tens","Ones"};
  int day[]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
  string names[]={"JAN","FEB","MAR","APR","MAY","JUN","JUL","AUG","SEP","OCT","NOV","DEC"};
  for(i=1;i<12;i++)
     day[i]+=day[i-1];            
  cin>>t;
  for(cn=1;cn<=t;cn++){
    cin>>s;
    s1=s.substr(0,2); d=atoi(s1.c_str());
    s2=s.substr(7,4); y=atoi(s2.c_str());
    s=s.substr(3,3);  
    if(isleap(y))  
       lp=1;
    else
       lp=0;
    for(i=0;i<12;i++){
      
       if(names[i].compare(s)==0)
          break;
    }
    
    n=0;
    if(i>0)
     n=day[i-1];
    n+=d;
  
    if(i>1 && lp==1){
         n++;      
    } 
    cout<<"Case "<<cn<<": ";  
    if(n<=300)
       cout<<n<<" "<<mth[0]<<endl;
    else if(n>300 && n<=360)
       cout<<n-300<<" "<<mth[1]<<endl;
    else 
       cout<<n-360<<" "<<mth[2]<<endl; 
  }
  return 0;
}
